Copper Creek offers the serenity of a quiet sanctuary while offering the benefits of living in proximity to the Las Vegas Strip. With the convenience of nearby shopping centers, business services, schools, and parks, Copper Creek is in a perfect location in Silverado Ranch. Minutes from the I-15, I-215, and McCarran International Airport, Copper Creek's location is ideal for both personal and professional lifestyles.<br>
<br>
Please visit our community and check out our spacious two bedroom Cedar Creek floor plan.<br>
